"{\"uid\": \"businesstoday.in-world-story-france-hit-by-another-sabotage-vandals-target-telecom-installations-amid-paris-olympics-2024-439289-2024-07-29\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home  Market  BT TV  Reels  Menu  France has been hit by another round of sabotage as vandals targeted multiple telecommunications lines.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.99975382079445, \"rank\": 0.0002373877370215977, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Installations belonging to French telecom companies SFR and Bouygues Telecom were vandalised on Sunday evening, the French Le Parisien newspaper reported on Monday.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8115466506270332, \"rank\": 0.23074176586443346, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bouygues Telecom\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bouygues_Telecom\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8115466506270332, \"rank\": 0.23074176586443346, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Le Parisien\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Le_Parisien\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cables had been cut in southern France, with installations near Luxembourg and Paris sabotaged.\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.99975382079445, \"rank\": 0.0002373877370215977, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\", \"score\": 0.9968342053379556, \"rank\": 0.0030370438799875716, \"text\": \"Luxembourg\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Luxembourg\"}, {\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.459645443497314e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Secretary of State for Digital Affairs Marina Ferrari confirmed the acts of vandalism, but said they had \\\"localised consequences\\\".\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Damages committed in several departments last night affected our telecommunications operators.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have localized consequences on access to fiber, fixed telephony and mobile telephony,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ferrari condemned in the strongest terms the \\\"cowardly and irresponsible acts\\\" and thanked the teams mobilised to carry out repairs and restore damaged sites to service.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferrari\", \"score\": 0.8914602006647792, \"rank\": 0.12175505799225998, \"text\": \"Ferrari\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferrari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferrari\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, train services were sabotaged in the country, which is hosting Olympics 2024.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sabotaged happened just as the Olympic Games were about to begin.France suspects members of far-left groups were behind the sabotage of the high-speed rail network last week, Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin said on Monday.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"score\": 0.9997053337076068, \"rank\": 0.00029259436431837904, \"text\": \"Interior Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Interior_minister\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"score\": 0.9999917501997208, \"rank\": 5.56632192365425e-06, \"text\": \"Gerald\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gerald_Ford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saboteurs struck the network on Friday with pre-dawn attacks on signal substations and cables at critical points, causing travel chaos hours before the opening ceremony in Paris.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.459645443497314e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have identified the profiles of several people,\\\" Darmanin told France 2 TV, adding that the sabotage bore the hallmarks of far-left groups.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutors office said no arrests had been made so far.\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.459645443497314e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A police official involved in the probe said it was \\\"too soon to tell\\\" if there was a link with acts of vandalism overnight that targeted the country's telecommunications network, Reuters reported.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1801, \"end\": 1808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.77992271257322e-13, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Living Media India Limited.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Living_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Living Media\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Living_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Living_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9610491517265749, \"rank\": 0.03980262220810533, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"d